Hi Fred,

No, this is not possible. On the other hand, the basic summary
statistics to estimate both LRR and SMD are the same. So, you can
repeat your analysis with SMD, if you want.

Given that you mentioned you have overlapping info. for participants
(due to repeated measurement over time and outcome) in some studies,
it would be useful to construct some form of a within-study (or within
whatever level that is appropriate in your case) var-covariance matrix
for effect estimates in such studies and feed it into the rma.mv()
function.

Kind regards,
Reza

